data.description:
$10k credit to Buyer towards closing costs or 2 - 1 buy down!  

This is the best price per square foot for a 4 bed, 2.5 bath, 3300 SF home in CDA! This spacious home in Hawks Nest has views of Canfield Mountain, room for RV parking, and AC. As you enter the home through the front door you are greeted to an open formal living room and dining room area with an adjacent alcove, perfect for a sideboard or dry bar. Past the dining room, you'll find a cozy family room / den, spacious eat-in kitchen, half bath and huge pantry/storage on the way to the garage.  Upstairs, every bedroom has a walk-in closet. The massive second floor flex room has much potential from a family room to a game room to an office with room for workout equipment  - or frame in a fifth bedroom!  

Whether you have a large family or need room for your pool table, shuffleboard, and arcades this is home for you!
